00:01:23.260 --> 00:01:24.980
Specifically bounded harmonic functions.

00:01:25.580 --> 00:01:27.700
Then he went to Berkeley, was assistent professor,

00:01:27.840 --> 00:01:29.760
showed amazing potential, then he moved to Montana

00:01:29.760 --> 00:01:31.620
and he blew the competition away.

00:01:32.120 --> 00:01:33.220
Yes, so who was he?

00:01:33.720 --> 00:01:34.480
Ted Kaczynski.

00:01:35.640 --> 00:01:36.320
Never heard of him.

00:01:36.600 --> 00:01:37.160
Hey, Timmy!

00:01:37.620 --> 00:01:38.120
Yo!

