00:01:48.040 --> 00:01:48.580
Yeah.

00:01:48.580 --> 00:01:50.040
He can contribute to the world and...

00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:50.880
and we can help him do that.

00:01:51.020 --> 00:01:53.560
